    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在舒缓的Lofi旋律中，构筑您的梦想空间，开启高效专注之旅。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lofi心居 </strong>是一款创新的<strong>游戏化专注工具</strong>与<strong>沉浸式装修模拟游戏</strong>的完美结合体 。这不仅仅是一个播放背景音乐的应用，更是一个您可以亲手打造、完全自定义的虚拟宁静空间。在这里，您可以通过布置房间、与宠物互动和完成目标，将枯燥的工作或学习时间，转化为充满成就感与治愈感的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏠 深度自由的装修模拟游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许高度定制化的房间装修，让你能打造独一无二的专属空间。你可以从海量的物品中选择和搭配，还可以修改颜色和材质，满足你的个性化需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/1ee751086026b39e5783cadab096a8ba.poster.avif?t=1770238752\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/1ee751086026b39e5783cadab096a8ba.webm?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/1ee751086026b39e5783cadab096a8ba.mp4?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎵 游戏化的高效专注工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们提供了海量的Lofi音乐与环境音效，作为您专注时的完美背景音，助您快速进入心流状态。同时，待办清单与番茄时钟等贴心工具，将为您的工作学习提供坚实助力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🐱 可爱的宠物伙伴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让可爱的虚拟宠物陪伴您度过每一段工作与学习时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/aec62699516f73f0f010f09c58255ad4.poster.avif?t=1770238752\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/aec62699516f73f0f010f09c58255ad4.webm?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/aec62699516f73f0f010f09c58255ad4.mp4?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌦️ 动态天气与氛围</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的动态天气系统，从明媚阳光到细雨绵绵，为您的工作空间提供不断变化的沉浸式氛围，匹配每一种心情与专注场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/0d5bc628c6ebf7021a67846467a22ecd.poster.avif?t=1770238752\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/0d5bc628c6ebf7021a67846467a22ecd.webm?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/0d5bc628c6ebf7021a67846467a22ecd.mp4?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🖼️ 沉浸式壁纸模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一键开启壁纸模式，将您精心打造的舒适房间变为桌面动态壁纸，让治愈的氛围延伸到您的现实屏幕，随时伴您左右。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/05ead24318e0a63343c57f2f9e8499e6.poster.avif?t=1770238752\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/05ead24318e0a63343c57f2f9e8499e6.webm?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003690/extras/05ead24318e0a63343c57f2f9e8499e6.mp4?t=1770238752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟 持续进化的舒适宇宙</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们承诺通过持续更新，不断扩展这个宁静宇宙：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多主题的家具、装饰与角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多品种的可爱宠物伙伴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天气、音效与游戏机制的深度联动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的社交与联机玩法</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮主要功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >悉心准备的Lofi音乐和各种环境音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To-do List和番茄时钟</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量的家具、物品、材质以用于搭建你的专属空间，房间内一切都可以定制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱且生动的猫咪（虽然有时候可能出现一些小问题🤭）</p></li></ul>",
